{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0072f8c4c0","title":"关于《毛泽东选集》注释等问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"beb3a6d028","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"0072f8c4c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d5dd4ebaaa","type":"title","text":"关于《毛泽东选集》注释等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"dcda73920a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、注释现在不要修改，这些人名都不要删掉，这些都是历史。没有司马炎、司马师、司马昭，荷以成为《普史》","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"0769f2d858","type":"paragraph","text":"二、《关于若干历史问题的决议》写得不好，可以不收。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"bcf0148662","type":"paragraph","text":"三、《整顿党的作风》中引用刘少奇的一段话没有必要，可以删去。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"0c8c2c8a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、新印《毛选》，仍用原来的日期。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"0ce5a98185","type":"paragraph","text":"五、《毛选》五、六两卷，一年以后再说，现在你们没有时间，我也没有时间","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"},{"id":"e4cf01bd14","type":"paragraph","text":"六、《语录》第二〇八页引用刘少奇的话的一段也删去；第二C八页标题“思想意识修养”改为“纠正错误思想”","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0"}],"page":{"id":"440b8afbd1","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0072f8c4c0","start":392,"end":392}}}},"__N_SSG":true}